            <thetext>Added a waypoint feature, which replaces the &quot;pageEnd&quot; event.

Please use:

var scrollContainer = this._getScrollContainer();
scrollContainer.setWaypointsY([&quot;100%&quot;]);

scrollContainer.addListener(&quot;waypoint&quot;,
function() {
  alert(&quot;waypoint reached&quot;);
});


You can add additional waypoint if you need them.</thetext>
